Plot
After overhearing the conversation between Gaeul and Uliminus (Chapter 16), she told Yuigard about that. Yuigard got angry at his brother because he thinks that you just have to use your full power end ends up throwing a piece of his chair on Phufun's face. She enjoyed the pain, indicating that she is a masochist. She tempted Yuigard to want the throne of the Demons. After his proposal to just fight against his brother, she was sure that he couldn't win, so she made a plan and told him about it. He was very pleased with her plan, thus he gave her the responsibility to carry out the plan.
